metadata.name: fix-webm-duration
metadata.author: Yuri Sitnikov <https://github.com/yusitnikov>
metadata.description: navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia + MediaRecorder create WEBM files without duration metadata. This library appends missing metadata section right to the file blob.

main.value: geogebra.jar geogebra_main.jar geogebra_gui.jar geogebra_properties.jar geogebra_export.jar geogebra_cas.jar geogebra_algos.jargeogebra_javascript.jar jlatexmath.jar jlm_greek.jar jlm_cyrillic.jar
